### 1. Criar usuário (sem auth)
POST http://localhost:3000/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dono@mesaflow.com",
  "name": "Dono Estabelecimento",
  "password": "senha123",
  "phone": "11987654321"
}

###

### 2. Login (gera access token + refresh token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dono@mesaflow.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### 3. Renovar access token (quando expirar)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI"
}

###

### 4. Verificar meus dados (rota protegida)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### 5. Logout (revoga refresh token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "refreshToken": "SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI"
}

###

### 6. Listar meu estoque (rota protegida)
GET http://localhost:3000/estoque
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

###

### 7. Criar item de estoque (rota protegida)
POST http://localhost:3000/estoque
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "nome": "Arroz 5kg",
  "quantidade": 50,
  "categoria": "Grãos",
  "fornecedor": "Distribuidora ABC"
}

###

### 8. Atualizar quantidade de estoque (rota protegida)
PUT http://localhost:3000/estoque/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "quantidade": 45
}

###

### 9. Deletar item de estoque (rota protegida)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/estoque/1
Authorization: Bearer SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI
